STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Michael J. RAMSEY, Defendant-Petitioner. C-208 September Term 2018
081054 Supreme Court of New Jersey. Clerk of the Supreme Court, October 18, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003130-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
